00:00:04,480 --> 00:00:07,420
Here’s another handy way to create Tab Stacks in Vivaldi.

2
00:00:08,040 --> 00:00:10,660
To create a tab stack by using tab selection,

3
00:00:10,760 --> 00:00:14,100
hold down the 'Shift' key and click on the tabs you'd like to include.

4
00:00:14,880 --> 00:00:18,080
Release ‘Shift’, and right-click on either
of the selected tabs,

5
00:00:18,100 --> 00:00:20,780
picking ‘New Tab from Selection’ from the menu.

6
00:00:31,540 --> 00:00:34,300
To ungroup your tabs, right-click on the Tab Stack

7
00:00:34,380 --> 00:00:38,100
and select 'Ungroup Tab Stack' to return to the default view.

